title: Once Were Warriors
overview: A family descended from Maori warriors is bedeviled by a violent father and the societal problems of being treated as outcasts.

title: A Clockwork Orange
overview: In the future, a sadistic gang leader is imprisoned and volunteers for a conduct-aversion experiment, but it doesn't go as planned.

title: Dogville
overview: A woman on the run from the mob is reluctantly accepted in a small Colorado community in exchange for labor, but when a search visits the town she finds out that their support has a price.

title: Pulp Fiction
overview: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster and his wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.

title: The Green Mile
overview: The lives of guards on Death Row are affected by one of their charges: a black man accused of child murder and rape, yet who has a mysterious gift.

title: Cool Hand Luke
overview: A laid back Southern man is sentenced to two years in a rural prison, but refuses to conform.

title: The Hateful Eight
overview: In the dead of a Wyoming winter, a bounty hunter and his prisoner find shelter in a cabin currently inhabited by a collection of nefarious characters.
stars: ['Samuel L. Jackson', 'Kurt Russell', 'Jennifer Jason Leigh', 'Walton Goggins']

title: The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo
overview: Journalist Mikael Blomkvist is aided in his search for a woman who has been missing for forty years by Lisbeth Salander, a young computer hacker.

title: Bir Zamanlar Anadolu'da
overview: A group of men set out in search of a dead body in the Anatolian steppes.

title: The Godfather: Part II
overview: The early life and career of Vito Corleone in 1920s New York City is portrayed, while his son, Michael, expands and tightens his grip on the family crime syndicate.

title: Andhadhun
overview: A series of mysterious events change the life of a blind pianist, who must now report a crime that he should technically know nothing of.

title: Carlito's Way
overview: A Puerto Rican former convict, just released from prison, pledges to stay away from drugs and violence despite the pressure around him and lead on to a better life outside of N.Y.C.

title: Witness for the Prosecution
overview: A veteran British barrister must defend his client in a murder trial that has surprise after surprise.

title: Primal Fear
overview: An altar boy is accused of murdering a priest, and the truth is buried several layers deep.

title: Scarface
overview: In 1980 Miami, a determined Cuban immigrant takes over a drug cartel and succumbs to greed.

title: Glengarry Glen Ross
overview: An examination of the machinations behind the scenes at a real estate office.

title: A Bronx Tale
overview: A father becomes worried when a local gangster befriends his son in the Bronx in the 1960s.

title: The Godfather: Part III
overview: Follows Michael Corleone, now in his 60s, as he seeks to free his family from crime and find a suitable successor to his empire.

title: Tengoku to jigoku
overview: An executive of a shoe company becomes a victim of extortion when his chauffeur's son is kidnapped and held for ransom.

title: Blood Simple
overview: The owner of a seedy small-town Texas bar discovers that one of his employees is having an affair with his wife. A chaotic chain of misunderstandings, lies and mischief ensues after he devises a plot to have them murdered.
